{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DjFuoZe7RKqFipZKrzLiMt","type":"tool_result","content":"   214→**Game Engine Alignment**\n   215→- [x] [engine] Create anchor-client package: `anchor build` → generate IDL, create `packages/anchor-client/` with typed exports for coinflip + platform programs, add `scripts/sync-idl` script that copies `target/idl/*.json` + `target/types/*.ts` into the package. Verify: package builds, types are importable, `pnpm lint` passes. (done: iteration 1)\n   216→- [ ] [engine] Align game-engine with on-chain: update `types.ts` (`COIN_SIDE_VALUES`: heads=0/tails=1; `COINFLIP_PHASE_VALUES`: created=0/ready=1/flipping=2/complete=3; tiers match spec). Rewrite `coinflip.ts` PDA derivation — delete BOLT ECS pool/entry/state PDAs, add `getMatchPda(creator)` + `getConfigPda()` matching on-chain seeds, update `PROGRAM_IDS` to real coinflip program ID. Verify: `pnpm lint` + `pnpm typecheck` pass in game-engine package.\n   217→\n   218→**Frontend Wiring**\n   219→- [ ] [frontend] Wire CoinflipContext to anchor-client: replace mock state management with on-chain program queries. Delete `mock-simulation.ts`. Wire `createMatch`/`joinMatch`/`cancelMatch`/`claimPayout` to real on-chain instructions via wallet-adapter. Verify: `pnpm lint` + `pnpm typecheck` pass in platform app.\n   220→- [ ] [frontend] Wire lobby browser: read open matches via `getProgramAccounts` with coinflip match account filter, implement tier filter + sort. Add error handling for insufficient balance, wallet disconnect, and transaction failure. Verify: `pnpm build` succeeds for platform app.\n   221→\n   222→### Scope Decisions\n   223→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7aeeab11-0053-463c-9811-f720a3b5ccf5","uuid":"36cbbfbd-f812-45eb-a709-804fc3cc902d","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/001-coinflip/spec.md","content":"**Game Engine Alignment**\n- [x] [engine] Create anchor-client package: `anchor build` → generate IDL, create `packages/anchor-client/` with typed exports for coinflip + platform programs, add `scripts/sync-idl` script that copies `target/idl/*.json` + `target/types/*.ts` into the package. Verify: package builds, types are importable, `pnpm lint` passes. (done: iteration 1)\n- [ ] [engine] Align game-engine with on-chain: update `types.ts` (`COIN_SIDE_VALUES`: heads=0/tails=1; `COINFLIP_PHASE_VALUES`: created=0/ready=1/flipping=2/complete=3; tiers match spec). Rewrite `coinflip.ts` PDA derivation — delete BOLT ECS pool/entry/state PDAs, add `getMatchPda(creator)` + `getConfigPda()` matching on-chain seeds, update `PROGRAM_IDS` to real coinflip program ID. Verify: `pnpm lint` + `pnpm typecheck` pass in game-engine package.\n\n**Frontend Wiring**\n- [ ] [frontend] Wire CoinflipContext to anchor-client: replace mock state management with on-chain program queries. Delete `mock-simulation.ts`. Wire `createMatch`/`joinMatch`/`cancelMatch`/`claimPayout` to real on-chain instructions via wallet-adapter. Verify: `pnpm lint` + `pnpm typecheck` pass in platform app.\n- [ ] [frontend] Wire lobby browser: read open matches via `getProgramAccounts` with coinflip match account filter, implement tier filter + sort. Add error handling for insufficient balance, wallet disconnect, and transaction failure. Verify: `pnpm build` succeeds for platform app.\n\n### Scope Decisions\n","numLines":10,"startLine":214,"totalLines":240}}}
