{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01XxEUkaJeyBmHYb9R4QTkbp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_0155bXgxz41N8x7f7NML8YiH","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/001-coinflip/history.md","old_string":"## Iteration 1 — 2026-02-18T06:40:45Z — COMPLETE\n- **Result**: All checklist items done, verification passed\n- **Log**: iteration-001.log","new_string":"## Iteration 1 — 2026-02-18T06:40:45Z — COMPLETE\n- **Result**: All checklist items done, verification passed\n- **Log**: iteration-001.log\n\n## Iteration 7 — 2026-02-18 — DONE\n- **Item**: Align game-engine with on-chain (types.ts + coinflip.ts)\n- **Changes**:\n  - `packages/game-engine/src/types.ts` — Updated `COIN_SIDE_VALUES` from `{heads: 1, tails: 2}` to `{heads: 0, tails: 1}` matching on-chain `SIDE_HEADS=0, SIDE_TAILS=1`\n  - `packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts` — Complete rewrite: removed all BOLT ECS PDAs (`derivePoolPDA`, `deriveCoinflipStatePDA`, `derivePlayerEntryPDA`, `deriveGameConfigPDA`), removed all instruction builders (`buildCreateMatchInstruction`, `buildJoinMatchInstruction`, `buildFlipCoinInstruction`, `buildClaimPayoutInstruction`), removed match status helpers and `CoinflipMatch`-dependent functions. Added `COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID` (real program ID from IDL), `getMatchPda(creator)` with seeds `[\"match\", creator]`, `getConfigPda()` with seeds `[\"coinflip_config\"]`. Kept helper functions: `getEntryAmount`, `calculatePotentialPayout`, `getOppositeSide`, `determineWinnerFromRandomness`.\n  - `packages/game-engine/src/index.ts` — Updated exports to match new coinflip.ts: removed deleted function/type exports, added `COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID`, `getMatchPda`, `getConfigPda`.\n- **Verification**: `pnpm lint` (17 packages, 0 errors) + `pnpm typecheck` (17 packages, all pass). No regressions."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_to